{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01GgTGuFZB67GPN53ms6pHdp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue now! The endpoints for the headless service only shows `notReadyAddresses` - this means the pod is in the headless service but marked as not-ready. \n\nIn Kubernetes, for a headless service, only **ready** pods are typically included in the DNS A records. Since `elasticsearch-0` is not ready (the readiness probe is failing because the cluster hasn't formed), it's not resolvable via DNS.\n\nThis creates a chicken-and-egg problem:\n1. ES can't form a cluster because it can't resolve peers via DNS\n2. ES can't become ready because it can't form a cluster\n\nThe fix is to add `publishNotReadyAddresses: true` to the headless service, which tells Kubernetes to include not-ready pods in DNS records - a standard pattern for StatefulSet-based distributed databases. Let me patch the service with this setting.\n\nI'm also checking the DNS search domains to verify how Elasticsearch resolves the headless service address.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":807,"cache_read_input_tokens":43391,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":807},"output_tokens":31,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b46e79cf-3f07-46ac-a7cf-24c58627c257","uuid":"db283851-2cac-4d98-9a3d-e5316a64df3f","request_id":"req_011CcLyiRMfE1H3GynMyHS3B"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01GgTGuFZB67GPN53ms6pHdp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issue is clear: the headless service only has `notReadyAddresses` because no pods are ready yet, causing DNS resolution to fail — a classic chicken-and-egg for distributed clusters. The fix is `publishNotReadyAddresses: true` on the headless service."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":807,"cache_read_input_tokens":43391,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":807},"output_tokens":31,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b46e79cf-3f07-46ac-a7cf-24c58627c257","uuid":"411cdbb6-2123-4872-8c42-bfeb7c239823","request_id":"req_011CcLyiRMfE1H3GynMyHS3B"}
